description:
In order to prevent Gaia from gaining more power, Yukito`s plan is to separate her from her kids. But Gaia was already prepared and summons the ultimate strange beast, Typhon. Despite their best efforts to flee, Yukito then gets devoured by it...
Source: crunchyroll

titles.title: We Know We Are Not Worthy O Great Lord Mitama in the Ancient Tim-

Ô déesse Mitama, à l’aube de l’univers, alors que les terres se formaient à peine, l’être divin, la déesse Mitama descendit en ce monde. Notre gratitude est infinie. Ô je t’implore, entends nos prières.
